{"tid":1964883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁志祥稱民建聯正考慮會否減薪　或捐部分薪金","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T06:51:40.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7dc06f16c308d7834df736f8762dcf92011394","tid":1964883,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥昨日宣布，她與全體司局長、特首辦主任減薪一成，為期一年。民建聯立法會議員梁志祥表示，支持問責官員減薪，與市民共渡時艱，民建聯正積極考慮會否減薪，但未知立法會制度是否容許即時減薪，如果不能減薪，傾向捐出部分薪金，建制派議員會再商量。<br />\n<br />\n梁志祥補充，民建聯議員早前已捐了薪金，成立基金支援失業人士，總數超過300萬元，但不便透露每人捐出的金額。他說，暫時未決定如果再捐出薪金是否同樣用作該黨的失業基金，但認為失業人士值得幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n被問到捐薪幅度是否一成，梁志祥說，捐贈模式因人而異，捐多捐少都可以，相信議員各自有標準，毋須劃一金額。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519773-20200409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519773-20200409.htm&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=718ef9fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519773-20200409.htm&h=9585a921\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519773-20200409.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯成功爭取自己減薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1035a39173abe97334ef1e57b903b01b8917ffa0","tid":1964883,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"經考慮後民建聯決定不會減薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b7627a301e5288f1ada08bc7d2b4fe7c9dfaf","tid":1964883,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"失業基金劉國勳有無得申請?"},{"pid":"2aad5e3ba300c73f9faa92c3d8cde0b3dee23fac","tid":1964883,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"捐俾邊個？捐國家不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fa7d1d07c1d30a93062864a0fbcc4ba97386e1","tid":1964883,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1035a39173abe97334ef1e57b903b01b8917ffa0","tid":1964883,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"經考慮後民建聯決定不會減薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"減1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會捐出去比人人有功練基金等廣大既支國同胞<br />\n洗到唔單止人人有書讀仲人人有功練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6581700a8c402bd8e928b55c6a6d410ef340c2","tid":1964883,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"捐就捐<br />\n唔捐就唔捐<br />\n冇人想知你考慮緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958f336ff4cad6ee9c7a0950897c273bb645a6ac","tid":1964883,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aad5e3ba300c73f9faa92c3d8cde0b3dee23fac","tid":1964883,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"捐俾邊個？捐國家不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"捐俾楊明燉湯鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aaf9017fc57fa31e2e6303070bcf73b3228636","tid":1964883,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"左手交右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}